styleCard.description: A steady, rhythmic piece that guides the listener through the diverse landscapes of Sri Lanka, blending traditional folk instrumentation with a cinematic atmosphere to evoke the spirit of discovery and cultural immersion. The Tamil road names inspire a deep connection to the local heritage.

directions: Go north on Opalgala Road (ஒப்பல்கல வீதி)
Turn right on Naula-Elahera-Pallegama-Hettipola Road (நாவுல-எலஹெர-பல்லேகம-ஹெட்டிபொல வீதி)
Turn right to stay on Naula-Elahera-Pallegama-Hettipola Road (நாவுல-எலஹெர-பல்லேகம-ஹெட்டிபொல வீதி)
Turn right on Theldeniyaya-Diwulapelessa Road (தெல்தெனிய-திவுல்பெலெஸ்ஸ வீதி)
Turn left on Mahiyanganaya-Dimbulagala-Dalukana Road (மகியங்கணை-திம்புலாகல-தளுக்கன வீதி)
Turn right on Dolakanda-Salasumgama Road (தொளக்கநதை-செலசும்கம வீதி)
Finish at Dolakanda-Salasumgama Road, Dehiattakandiya, 32150, on the right
